                    <h2 class="entry-title-h entry-title-prial-h"><a rel="bookmark" title="Why Striving for Salvation Won\'t Save You" href="http://www.christianpost.com/news/why-striving-for-salvation-wont-save-you-134156/?>" class="h52">Why Striving for Salvation Won't Save You</a></h2>
                                            <div class="entry-meta-h">
                            <span class="entry-byline-h">By <a href="/author/dan-delzell/">Dan Delzell</a></span>
                        </div>
                                    </header>
                <div class="entry-content-h">
                    <p>Millions of people strive for salvation, while finding no rest in their unending efforts. At the same time, millions of others rest in their salvation, while then earnestly living for the one who died and rose to save them. So what's the difference?</p>
                </div>
