            <h1 class="title-headline-main"><a href="http://www.christianpost.com/news/the-benham-brothers-decry-growing-threat-to-religious-freedoms-if-christians-dont-stand-up-it-will-turn-into-persecution-for-our-children-134400/" class="h24">The Benham Brothers Decry Growing Threat to Religious Freedoms: If Christians Don't Stand Up, It Will Turn Into Persecution for Our Children</a></h1>
